title: Coast to coast AM 2011-04-15 Spiritual Enlightenment
description:
Coast to coast AM 2011-04-15 
"Spiritual Enlightenment"
Date: 04-15-11 
Host: George Noory 
Guests: Hazel Courteney, Open Lines 
In the middle two hours, journalist and author Hazel Courteney shared details from her life-changing spiritual awakening, as well as her unique insights into science, the Big Bang, consciousness, and God. 

The final hour featured Open Lines, with a special 'nice line' for callers to talk about the greatest thing somebody has ever done for them or that they have done for someone else. 

News segment guests: Lauren Weinstein, Jeff Nelken, Steve Shenk
